how to set up a new ubuntu machine:

1, download ubuntu 20.04 from website and create a bootable usb stick.

2, use the usb to start a new machine and install.

3, download vim :

4, ~/.bashrc  ~/.vimrc

5, git clone https://github.com/VundleVim/Vundle.vim.git ~/.vim/bundle/Vundle.vim

6, how to resize?

df -h

lsblk

sudo growpart /dev/nvme0n1 1

resize2fs /dev/root
